data.description: Nestled in a picturesque setting, this 2,426 sq. ft. home boasts an additional spacious 912 sq. ft. garage. Featuring two completed bedrooms and a full bath, the house offers a canvas for personalized touches, with an unfinished basement and upstairs area awaiting your creative vision. Appraiser estimated the home as 1,700 sq feet finished.  The property includes two powerful 75,000 BTU HVAC systems and a 100,000 BTU heater, ensuring comfort in all seasons. Outside, lush grass complements stunning golf course views, with the lake just a minute's walk away. Additionally, there's a large shed and a massive two-car garage/workshop area, perfect for hobbies and storage. With the potential to add a boat slip, this property has all the elements to transform into your dream home.
